# Account Settings

In this tab, you can view your account settings as well as the linked WhatsApp Business account and its supported capabilities. \
\
You can easily access it through **Dashboard \> Settings \> Account**

![Account Settings](/account.png)

## WABA Health Overview

A concise overview of the features and service capabilities available on your account.

| Detail             | Description                                                                                           |
| ------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Phone ID           | The unique identifier of the connected WhatsApp Business Account (WABA).                              |
| Phone Number       | The phone number associated with your WABA.                                                           |
| Account Status     | Displays your service activation status (Active or Inactive).                                         |
| Phone Quality      | Indicates the quality rating of the phone number connected to your WABA (Low, Medium, High).          |
| Messaging Limits   | The maximum number of customers your service can message per day (e.g., 250 customers/day).           |
| AI Chat Bot Limits | The number of AI chatbot requests that can be handled within a given period (e.g., 10 requests/hour). |

## (App Name) Account

Settings and details for your connected WhatsApp Business Account.

| Detail | Description                                     |
| ------ | ----------------------------------------------- |
| Name   | The display name of your account.               |
| Email  | The email address associated with your account. |

## Account Utilities

Manage essential actions related to your account, including password reset and organization removal.

| Detail              | Description                                                                     |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Reset Password      | A button that allows you to reset your account.                                 |
| Delete Organization | A button that permanently deletes your organization linked to the WABA account. |
